Description

The ChicagoPizzaController is a controller for the Chicago pizza window.

The Crust enum class is a class to store the crust as constants.

NYPizza
NYPizza is a concrete class that implements the abstract class PizzaFactory and creates instances of Pizza and the subclass type.

The NYPizzaController is a controller for the New York pizza window.
Order
The Order class is a class that will create an order of pizzas.
Pizza
The Pizza class creates an instance of pizza and sets th crust and toppings accordingly.
PizzaFactory
The PizzaFactory interface is responsible for creating types of pizzas and is used in the Chicago Pizza and New York Pizza classes.
ProjectFourController
The ProjectFourController is a controller class for the entire project.
ProjectFourMain
The ProjectFourMain class is the driver class for the project.
Size
The Size enum class is a class to store the size as constants.
StoreOrder
The StoreOrder class is a class that is responsible for storing Order objects into an StoreOrder object and exporting the orders.
StoreOrdersController
The StoreOrderController class is responsible for storing all orders placed by users and has features such as removing an order or exporting all orders to a text file.
Topping
The Topping enum class is a class to store the toppings as constants.
